        void addEmails(String id,
               Set<String> emails)

        id - must be non-null and non-blank
        emails - must be non-null and elements must be non-blank

      • removeEmails

        void removeEmails(String id,
                  Set<String> emails)
        Remove a set of emails that have been associated with an ID. Removing an email that is not associated with an ID is a no-op.
        Parameters:
        id - must be non-null and non-blank
        emails - must be non-null and elements must be non-blank

      • removeEmail

        void removeEmail(String id,
                 String email)
        Remove an email that has been associated with an ID. Removing an email that is not associated with an ID is a no-op.
        Parameters:
        id - must be non-null and non-blank
        email - must be non-null

        Returns:
